{"tid":1452432,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[毛語錄] [文宣］槍桿子裏出政權!","createTime":"2019-08-12T01:16:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T06:07:55.000Z","uid":123713,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a59012ee89437475628a8afee1df68ac68ef14d2","tid":1452432,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:16:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dQVUa67.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdQVUa67.jpg&h=227a58e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n連登仔一向愛國愛港，唔似BK呢類反亂基地。<br />\n我同大家一樣繫香港<br />\n所以今日想同大家一齊溫習毛語錄<br />\n重溫毛主席既偉大思想<br />\n<br />\n以下節錄幾句我認為講得特別好<br />\n歡迎同學傳閱同討論<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<br />\n我們這個隊伍完全是為著人民的，是徹底地為人民的利益工作的。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n究竟是一個黨好，還是幾個黨好？現在看來，恐怕是幾個黨好。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n革命不是請客吃飯，不是做文章，不是繪畫綉花，不能那樣雅致，那樣從容不迫，&ldquo;文質彬彬&rdquo;，那樣&ldquo;溫良恭儉讓&rdquo;。革命就是暴動，是一個階級推翻一個階級的暴烈的行動。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n鬥爭，失敗，再鬥爭，再失敗，再鬥爭，直至勝利－－這就是人民的邏輯，他們也是決不會違背這個邏輯的。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n加強紀律性,革命無不勝。</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"07b1b8bf15c5d9fa81668a7ef3851f444113eaed","tid":1452432,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:17:09.000Z","msg":"屌明明想開係學術台"},{"pid":"d1134475837731aa1c77461b5c2e0374e361c8c6","tid":1452432,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:21:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aa17afc0a3cf5701485d9fa29a171f0e38ae452b","tid":1452432,"uid":276941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a59012ee89437475628a8afee1df68ac68ef14d2","tid":1452432,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:16:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dQVUa67.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdQVUa67.jpg&h=227a58e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n連登仔一向愛國愛港，